Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:07.03,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I finally made it here…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:09.52,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Hasunosora!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:13.52,Rurino,,0,0,0,,After a year and a half, I’m back in Japan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:16.56,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Y’know, I didn’t expect this…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:18.56,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I see…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:20.93,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It’s kinda hot, huh!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:25.48,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Wait, it’s even hotter here than in California!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:30.49,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It’s so… humid and muggy…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.35,0:00:40.07,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yep, this is a Japanese summer, alright…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:45.19,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Hm? What?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.43,0:00:47.38,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You need somethin’?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:51.63,Rurino,,0,0,0,,‘Kay, ‘kay, what is it, most welcome foreign guest?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:01:00.34,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You wanna know how to get from here to Kanazawa?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.79,0:01:01.63,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Uh, well!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:03.13,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.35,0:01:05.47,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Little wait, please!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:08.24,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Uh…! Um…!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.61,0:01:10.62,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This! This way!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:13.23,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go straight! Over!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:15.04,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, yes!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:17.45,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, okay!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:18.66,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:20.61,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you, thank you!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:22.55,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, yes!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:24.30,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You’re welcome!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:27.20,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Oh?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:37.09,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Are you inviting me to take a taxi together if I’m also going to Kanazawa Station…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:40.10,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Mm…!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:41.47,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you, thank you!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.81,0:01:43.80,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bye-bye! Goodbye!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:46.73,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good luck! Have a nice day!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.05,0:01:50.92,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Haa…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:55.45,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should’ve said yes…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:02:00.85,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But I don’t think I can last inside a car like that…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:04.29,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Never know when I’ll run out of battery…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:06.30,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Welp…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:10.98,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Guess I’m taking the bus alone…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.47,0:02:16.30,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But I’m looking forward to this…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:20.43,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Hasunosora School Idol Club.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…I hope I’ll have a fun time there.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:43.31,Kaho,,0,0,0,,It was really cool seeing you and \NTsuzuri-senpai on stage together~…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:46.23,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:50.98,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But Kaho-san, while I am glad to hear you say that…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:54.84,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That was a while ago now, you know?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:03:00.85,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I remember it like it was yesterday~…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:03.82,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Good memory.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.22,0:03:05.38,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,You’re very smart.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:08.42,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I don’t think that’s what she meant…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:14.08,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,We’ve gained quite a number of \Nsubscribers on our channel recently.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
