Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:23.09,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Why are you two encouraging me so forcefully?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:25.80,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Nice, Kozu.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:28.90,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Not you too! Knock it off!\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:34.05,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It looks like you’re fully back to your usual self, Kozue-senpai.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.30,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I think so too, Sayaka-san.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:43.33,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’ve caused a great deal of trouble for you all,\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:45.84,Kozue,,0,0,0,,but I am truly grateful.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:51.75,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,No, it’s okay. Don’t worry about it, K-Kozue-senpai.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:57.17,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I’m glad you two are getting closer!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:00.14,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And that’s why…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:06.31,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I think it’d be a great time to invite new members to the club!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:09.23,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,New members?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:10.90,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.90,0:04:16.30,Kaho,,0,0,0,,“Dream Believers” is really a song for three subunits to sing, right?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.92,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Oh, that’s what you mean.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:22.06,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Right!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:28.16,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And because of that, if we get some new members, we’ll be able to have a perfect performance of “Dream Believers”!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.62,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that’d look like!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:35.41,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I’m sure it would be an even more amazing performance!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:39.28,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Another subunit, huh…\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:46.50,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Well, no matter the case, we might get new members with the new batch of students next year.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:50.31,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh!? I can’t wait that long!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:54.04,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Where can we find new members…?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:58.29,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tsuzuri-senpai, you wouldn’t happen to have two twin sisters, would you?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.93,0:05:01.71,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Don’t say something so terrifying…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.61,Kozue,,0,0,0,,What a nightmare.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:06.45,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,What am I to you?\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.10,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Excuse meeee!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:16.43,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Is this the School Idol Club!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:20.03,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, it is…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.42,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But, who are you…?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:25.30,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Osawa Rurino! And I’m looking to join!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:27.08,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We…\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:29.40,Kaho,,0,0,0,,We got a new applicant~!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:40.71,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m Osawa Rurino, and this month, I transferred to Hasunosora!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:42.72,Rurino,,0,0,0,,That makes me the firstest of first-years!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:48.15,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Huh… So you’ve been going to school in California until just recently.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.31,Rurino,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.31,0:05:56.44,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I actually planned to come in during summer break, but I couldn’t wait any longer so I dipped!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:58.57,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ah, I mean I decided to return immediately!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:03.11,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It’s alright, you don’t need to be so stiff.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:05.92,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Just speak as you normally would.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.50,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.45,Kaho,,0,0,0,,It’s nice to meet you, Rurino-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:12.89,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Alright, I’ll take you up on that, then!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:16.10,Rurino,,0,0,0,,What’s up? You can call me Ruri for short!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:18.22,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Hiya, Ruri.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.10,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You certainly are adaptable…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:23.40,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Um…\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:26.13,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,It’s a pleasure to meet you, Rurino-san.\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:28.93,Kaho,,0,0,0,,So anyway, Rurino-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:30.63,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Why’d you decide to come here?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:34.48,Kaho,,0,0,0,,And also, what made you decide to become a school idol!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:37.86,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m interested in that as well.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:41.51,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Could it have been… our recent performance?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:45.04,Rurino,,0,0,0,,‘Cuz it seemed fun!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:48.27,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,I-It seemed fun…?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:50.26,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I totally get you!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.34,Kaho,,0,0,0,,School idols are amazing, right!?\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:54.32,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:07:00.88,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You were all fired up like, “wow!” and then you felt so cool, like, “whoa!” and you were all so sparkly and shiny!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:07.58,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I thought you all shone so bright! It was so impressive how amazing you were!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Cogito! Ergo Ruri!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.47,0:07:14.26,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Right, right!? That’s exactly it!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:18.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And I love having fun,\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:24.20,Rurino,,0,0,0,,so I thought that I really wanted to be a school idol and I rushed back here!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:26.42,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I see…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:31.57,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But you came to think that way from watching a broadcast of our performance, right?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:33.52,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m glad to hear it.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:35.97,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Nice, Kozu.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.67,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Again, that’s enough of that.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:42.98,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your application, Rurino-san.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:44.74,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I accept.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:50.43,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Hm… though, seeing as you’ve just transferred in,\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.43,0:07:55.13,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I suppose starting you off with our full regimen might be too much, huh?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:58.01,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You’re still getting accustomed to your new classes, too.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:01.77,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You… have a point!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:07.15,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I believe we should start you off on a trial period.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:11.41,Kozue,,0,0,0,,That way, you can freely attend whenever you have the time.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.87,0:08:15.04,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You can steadily grow accustomed to being a member of our club.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:18.29,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Thanks for lookin’ out for me!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:22.47,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve got no problem with that, so I’m {\i1}all welcome {\i0}to it!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:28.02,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Actually, I’m thankful you didn’t have me go through some sort of entrance exam!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:33.91,Kaho,,0,0,0,,If there was something like that, I wouldn’t be here, ahaha~\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:37.15,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,You shouldn’t be proud of that!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:39.49,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ahaha!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:44.98,Rurino,,0,0,0,,‘Kay then! Lookin’ forward to joining you guys as a trial member!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.32,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
